text: Breñon is a corregimiento in Renacimiento District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 755 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 532; its population as of 2000 was 648. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
